public class ShanksException
extends Exception

This exception include all possible exceptions that can be generated on the hole simulation framework. It is intended to unify all throws exception declaration to make statements more legible.

ShanksException

public ShanksException(String message,
                       Throwable cause)
This have to bee the more used constructor, cause a ShanksException its really whole prosibilitie of other exceptions. So when need to create one Shanks exception it is necessary to pass to the new exception object all fields and characteristic from the original exception.

Parameters:
message - the message of the original exception.
cause - the original exception object.
